* Martin Gimm: Zur Entstehungsgeschichte des "P'ei-wen yün-fu": Kurze Addenda. T'oung Pao , Second Series, Vol. 70, Livr. 4/5 (1984), pp. 279-286  [[@http://www.jstor.org/stable/4528318|JSTOR]]
 